==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|head=[[machine]] [[translation]]}}

# {{context|translation studies}} The act of [[translate|translating]] something by means of a [[machine]], especially a [[computer]].
# {{context|translation studies}} The act of translating a [[computer language]] into a form more directly usable by the computer.

